org.conqat.lib.commons.region

Class OffsetBasedRegion

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.conqat.lib.commons.region.SimpleRegion
      • org.conqat.lib.commons.region.OffsetBasedRegion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<SimpleRegion>

    public class OffsetBasedRegion
extends SimpleRegion
    Marker class used in code that needs to work with both offset- and line-based regions to avoid confusing them. Offsets are inclusive (both start and end) and 0-based.
    See Also:
